    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You use your shield to conceal your own body language and keep your attention focused.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Shield Focus, base attack bonus +6 or fighter level 4th, Sense Motive 1 rank.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You add your shield's bonus to AC to the DC of feint attempts against you.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 5 stamina points to force a foe to attempt two Bluff checks when trying to feint against you in combat, and use the lower of the two results. (See page 18.)",
